  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I remember there was the-- [NON-ENGLISH] was working-- different nationalities working on different lines of-- some are making the, the floors, and the [INAUDIBLE], some different--",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My job was the garden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So did you meet Khruschev?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I meet him twice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, he talked to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was not the, the-- in this time, he was only in the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was the secretary of Ukraine, not in the secretary of Russia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later on, he was in Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah, here I talk with him, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He asked about, how was it in the partisans?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I have a vodka with him, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And did you have other jobs there, in, in Kiev, after the war?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After, after I went [BACKROUND NOISE] away from there because it was not a good place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very isolated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I went away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- and I find the-- a, a, a person, was Marchenko.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Marchenko, he was in the partisans, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was the head of [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I went to him, and he, he gave me a job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He gave me a job, [NON-ENGLISH] means to, to, to, to-- oh boy, I have to look to bring what they need for the-- for the shops, for the-- to bring some machinery or else in, in this.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I have to find-- for them, it's-- you have to find.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This is you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And what I have to do, I have to-- from the, the army, from the-- from the tankers, I buy [LAUGHS] oil from the tanks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They threw away barrels of oil from, from from, from the army when they, they come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
